title: Angel and Faith 25 (2013) (Tablet Edition)
description:
I adjusted the resolution and compression of the original scan for easier reading on tablets and to save space. All credit goes to the original scanner for their hard work. I have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.



Angel and Faith 25

By:   	Christos Gage, Rebekah Isaacs, Dan Jackson	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Action-Adventure, Horror
Series:   	Angel
Publisher:   	Dark Horse	
Pub. Date:  	August 28, 2013
Format:         CBZ

Millions of lives hang in the balance, and Angel and Faith just might be on the losing end of this battle. It's times like these that call for drastic measures . . . How far will they go to save the world?

Lives are lost, heroes are born, and as one chapter ends, another begins.
